  <p align="left">Dear Maria,</p>
  <p align="left">Thanks for your letter. I <font color="#0000ff"><input id="q1" type="droptarget"/> your family is okay and <font color="#0000ff"><input id="q2" type="droptarget"/></font> affected too badly <font color="#0000ff"><input id="q3" type="droptarget"/></font> the awful floods last week.</font></p>
  <p align="left">In your letter you ask for advice about ways of raising money for the disaster and I've <font color="#0000ff"><input id="q4" type="droptarget"/> up with a few ideas. I <font color="#0000ff"><input id="q5" type="droptarget"/></font> advise you to ask for donations because people might be suspicious that the money won't get to <font color="#0000ff"><input id="q6" type="droptarget"/></font> victims. It's also not very easy to ask people for money like this.</font></p>
  <p align="left">If I <font color="#0000ff"><input id="q7" type="droptarget"/> you, I'd try to organize <font color="#0000ff"><input id="q8" type="droptarget"/></font> sponsored walk or run. I'm sure you could get lots of students from your university involved. You don't <font color="#0000ff"><input id="q9" type="droptarget"/></font> to do too much for this. You <font color="#0000ff"><input id="q10" type="droptarget"/></font> just make sure people have enough time to get as many sponsors as possible before the event. If you want to do something in addition to <font color="#0000ff"><input id="q11" type="droptarget"/></font>, I'd <font color="#0000ff"><input id="q12" type="droptarget"/></font> you to hold a bring-and-buy sale. All you need to do is book a hall and get as many of <font color="#0000ff"><input id="q13" type="droptarget"/></font> friends involved as you can.</font></p>
  <p align="left">However, I <font color="#0000ff"><input id="q14" type="droptarget"/> you should be aware that people can sometimes be unreliable and not turn up to events or not give you <font color="#0000ff"><input id="q15" type="droptarget"/></font> money they promised, so you'd <font color="#0000ff"><input id="q16" type="droptarget"/></font> not start working out how much you've raised until they've actually given <font color="#0000ff"><input id="q17" type="droptarget"/></font> to you.</font></p>
  <p align="left">Anyway, I <font color="#0000ff"><input id="q18" type="droptarget"/> you the very best of luck and don't <font color="#0000ff"><input id="q19" type="droptarget"/></font> to get in touch if you'd <font color="#0000ff"><input id="q20" type="droptarget"/></font> me to help in any way. I love walking!</font></p>
  <p align="left">With love, </p>
  <p align="left">Melissa</p>
